4725c769e","tid":504507,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T17:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c9aa628b843458902c0782b7c59c315e136107","tid":504507,"uid":61271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T17:14:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/10/21/two-diet-drinks-a-day-could-double-the-risk-of-diabetes-study-fi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fnews%2F2016%2F10%2F21%2Ftwo-diet-drinks-a-day-could-double-the-risk-of-diabetes-study-fi%2F&d=Xg0MilhLFswsUtwzR4mAVEzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=964e89ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/10/21/two-diet-drinks-a-day-could-double-the-risk-of-diabetes-study-fi/</a><br />\n<br />\nTwo fizzy drinks a day could double the risk of diabetes - even if they are diet versions - a Swedish study has found.<br />\n<br />\nResearch by the Karolinska Institute on 2,800 adults found that those who consumed at least two 200ml servings of soft drinks daily were 2.4 times as likely to suffer from a form of type 2 diabetes.<br />\n<br />\n轉用代糖未必真係健康咗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIt was also possible that those consuming low calorie drinks may have switched to them after a long history of drinking sugary versions, which could explain the link with diabetes, he added.<br />\n<br />\nConsumers of soft drinks were likely to have a lifestyle which was less healthy overall, a factor which the study tried to adjust for.<br />\n<br />\n而且個study係retrospective做<br />\n<br />\n如果要準確比較，要做番個RCT"},{"pid":"ad9a72bf9a8a904948d18a748c3f6250d5fe326e","tid":504507,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T17:15:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大學讀CHEM時Professor話齋: 飲正常可樂十日後爆血管,飲代糖十年後生癌,死快D定死慢D既分別</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個prof講野有無證據先?"},{"pid":"504aeec9b6d115cf4bd6354cdf411a22ffd98ae3","tid":504507,"uid":41846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T18:04:41.000Z","msg":"飲乜野食乜野過量都係唔健康㗎啦<br />\n但係聽聞過人工代糖會影響心血管<br />\n同時有唔少天然食品都含有所謂嘅人工代糖<br />\n所以其實唔食過量都冇問題我覺得"},{"pid":"cd64360699f8a93c2cbc0b8e1a5a975c32ea9802","tid":504507,"uid":74598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T18:09:20.000Z","msg":"糖係咪有害？"},{"pid":"055763b83df6d659a5014f6290f01e3fd4559287","tid":504507,"uid":107157,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T18:36:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>糖係咪有害？</blockquote><br />\n糖係一種會addicted既物質，其他食物多數越食會越厭，因為大腦傾向你吸收更多唔同既營養，所以人類先會咩都想食，又係咁想試新野，但係糖就例外，因為糖份係原始生活係極度重要，珍貴既野，好多時要靠其他食物形式轉化成糖竹，唔似而家咁係直接以unbranched 既形式吸收，佢亦同時支持身體由其是大腦既活動，所以會令人越食越想食，同毒品一樣上癮，亦都因為咁解釋到甜品放係第2個胃既原因。"},{"pid":"114e93b40e851f0870ed0ef8100d66daea48ff6a","tid":504507,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T18:39:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>糖係咪有害？</blockquote><br />\n糖係一種會addicted既物質，其他食物多數越食會越厭，因為大腦傾向你吸收更多唔同既營養，所以人類先會咩都想食，又係咁想試新野，但係糖就例外，因為糖份係原始生活係極度重要，珍貴既野，好多時要靠其他食物形式轉化成糖竹，唔似而家咁係直接以unbranched 既形式吸收，佢亦同時支持身體由其是大腦既活動，所以會令人越食越想食，同毒品一樣上癮，亦都因為咁解釋到甜品放係第2個胃既原因。</blockquote><br />\n利申： medic yr 4"}]}